{
  "stem": "13911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We look out, you know, every day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime-- I must-- this I must say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, this was in the dead ghetto, where I came-- they brought me in the dead ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, we looked through the-- because the attic was wooden planks, like.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in between the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Between the-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, the cracks between-- we look out, to see what's happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You could see the living ghetto, and it's an inferno.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole ghetto's on fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened there-- because they were the living ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's all tricks, you know, which eased their way to accomplish what they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When-- when-- when the dead ghetto-- you know, like, it took 15 days, but, of course, 19,000 were taken, put on trucks, and brought to the mass graves which were ready, waiting for them.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these graves-- like, a few weeks, maybe-- two, three weeks before, Jews were taken-- like, this was another forced labor-- taken to dig-- to dig graves.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they called it-- they say they are preparing for an airport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What airport will be needed in our city?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was for an airport-- ein Flugplatz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is what-- But, of course, Jewish intuition-- they knew what-- what-- they knew what-- what it meant.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were mass graves. 19,000 were buried in one-- gigantic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they took-- labor was cheap, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they took as many men as-- and-- and 19,000 were buried in that grave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, in the-- in the living ghetto, they saw these trucks, passing by, loaded like cattle, like sardines, you know, packed as-- the more the better, you know?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Bringing them to [INAUDIBLE], that place where the mass graves stood.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
